               <msContents>
                  <summary>Ziq Chants, መጽሐፈ፡ ዚቅ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="92r" facs="003">Fols 1r–92r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1979Mashaf">Maṣḥafa ziq</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                       ናሁ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ጽሒፈ፡ ዚቅ፡ እምዮሐንስ፡ እስከ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ዘጐንደር፡ መልክዓ፡ ሥላሴ ለገበዋቲክሙ፡ ዚቅ፡ ወአንተኒ፡ ሕፃን፡ ነቢየ፡ ልዑል፡ ትሰመይ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
